---
title: Creamy Turkey and Bacon Linguine with Spinach and Parmesan
description: Here's an easy, breezy dinner inspired by a restaurant classic: alfredo! Italian-seasoned turkey roasts in the oven, while an irresistible Parmesan cream sauce simmers away. Bacon, spinach and linguine make this meal a dream!
